metadata.name: Believer Special Edition #1
metadata.description:
Believers Special Edition of 15/15

Believers, is a collection that talk about mens and womens who walk past a wall. It is up to us viewers to decide if everyone's lives are real or if we are just witnessing the illusion of life flowing by. The question is, do we believe what we see?  
"We believe in the images when the images itself reflect what we want to see."  
Joan Fontcuberta
